{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 271 "3.  Fund
amental Theorem of Algebra.  The Fundamental Theorem of Algebra assert
s that every non-constant polynomial (with complex-valued coefficients
) has a root (a zero, a solution).  A consequence of the Fundamental T
heorem of Algebra is that every polynomial of degree " }{TEXT 276 1 "n
" }{TEXT -1 13 " has exactly " }{TEXT 277 1 "n" }{TEXT -1 108 " roots.
  An alternate formulation of this consequence would be that every non
-constant polynomial of degree " }{TEXT 279 1 "n" }{TEXT -1 38 " can b
e factored into a product of a  " }{TEXT 278 1 "n" }{TEXT -1 16 " line
ar factors." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
-1 35 "Consider the following polynomials:" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
-1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 6 "I.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "f := x^3
-x^2-2*x" "6#>%\"fG,(*$%\"xG\"\"$\"\"\"*$F'\"\"#!\"\"*&F+F)F'F)F," }
{TEXT -1 15 "         II.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "g := 6*x^3+11*x^2+6*x+1
" "6#>%\"gG,**&\"\"'\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"$F(F(*&\"#6F(*$F*\"\"#F(F(*&F'F(F
*F(F(F(F(" }{TEXT -1 24 "                 III.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "h :
= x^3-5*x+x^2-5;" "6#>%\"hG,**$%\"xG\"\"$\"\"\"*&\"\"&F)F'F)!\"\"*$F'
\"\"#F)F+F," }{TEXT -1 19 "                   " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 7 "IV.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "F := x^4-144" "6#>%\"FG,&*$%\"xG
\"\"%\"\"\"\"$W\"!\"\"" }{TEXT -1 19 "             V.    " }{XPPEDIT 
19 1 "G := 3*x^4+4*x^3-2*x^2+x-6;" "6#>%\"GG,,*&\"\"$\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"
%F(F(*&F+F(*$F*F'F(F(*&\"\"#F(*$F*F/F(!\"\"F*F(\"\"'F1" }{TEXT -1 15 "
         VI.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "H := x^5-x^2-2*x" "6#>%\"HG,(*$%\"xG
\"\"&\"\"\"*$F'\"\"#!\"\"*&F+F)F'F)F," }{TEXT -1 24 "                 \+
       " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 257 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 
172 "Factor each polynomial and determine whether Maple was able to fi
nd enough linear factors to demonstrate the above assertion about the \+
appropriate number of linear factors." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "
" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 17 "f:='x^3-x^2-2*x':" }}}
{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 24 "g:='6*x^3+11*x^2+6*x+1':" }}
}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 19 "h:='x^3-5*x+x^2-5':" }}}
{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 13 "F:='x^4-144':" }}}{EXCHG 
{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 27 "G:='3*x^4+4*x^3-2*x^2+x-6':" }}}
{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 19 "H:='x^5-x^2-2*x':\n\n" }}}
{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 20 "factor(x^3-x^2-2*x);" }}
{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#*(%\"xG\"\"\",&F$F%F%F%F%,&F$F%\"\"#!
\"\"F%" }}}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" 
{MPLTEXT 1 0 27 "factor(6*x^3+11*x^2+6*x+1);" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" 
