with roots   -2, 5, 5, " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "-1/2" "6#,$*&\"\"\"F%\"\"#!\"
\"F'" }{TEXT -1 71 ", 1+I and  1-I.  (Here the \"5, 5\" indicates that
 5 is a \"double root\".)" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG 
{PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 52 "expand((x+2)*(x-5)^2*(x+1/2)*(x-(1-
I))*((x-(1+I))));" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#,0\"#]\"\"\"*&\"#
