{PARA 257 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 27 "Factor each polynomial and " }{TEXT 
307 9 "determine" }{TEXT -1 156 " whether Maple was able to find enoug
h linear factors to demonstrate the above assertion about the appropri
ate number of linear factors.   Did you do this??" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 37 "Did not factor G into lin
ear factors." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
-1 3 "6/6" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 3 "4/6" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
